427
00:22:16,503 --> 00:22:18,088
- You don't think
utilizing stem cells

428
00:22:18,129 --> 00:22:20,298
to cure one of the
deadliest forms of cancer

429
00:22:20,340 --> 00:22:22,217
is complicated?

430
00:22:22,258 --> 00:22:24,010
Quite self-assured, are we?

