you can beat death.

434
00:22:32,185 --> 00:22:34,979
Otherwise, what's the point
of doing what we do?

435
00:22:35,021 --> 00:22:36,690
- Well...

436
00:22:38,483 --> 00:22:40,652
- How was surgery?
- Perfect.

437
00:22:40,694 --> 00:22:42,737
- Perfect? Excellent.

