00:22:42,779 --> 00:22:45,990
I heard it went a little long.

439
00:22:46,032 --> 00:22:47,450
- You heard?

440
00:22:47,492 --> 00:22:50,203
- Mm-hmm. I did.

441
00:22:50,245 --> 00:22:52,122
- A little long?

442
00:22:54,165 --> 00:22:56,668
Do you mind if I ask
who you heard that from?

